# DeployOps line-ending policy
# The deployed app is a single CRLF index.html. Lock it so editors,
# patches, and any future auto-sync run can never drift it to LF or
# produce mixed endings (the 312-line churn we just cleaned up).

*.html text eol=crlf

# Leave everything else to git's defaults. Add more lines here only
# if a new tracked text type starts showing line-ending churn.
